{"tid":924013,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"點解王傑把聲可以變得咁誇張?","createTime":"2018-12-01T17:52:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-03T14:40:58.000Z","uid":70335,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"d3a19e8a8d0a65be2cff1b8e9a5facc868b9f94f","tid":924013,"uid":70335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T17:52:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/5rnw-4Fu9is\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F5rnw-4Fu9is&d=8o05Qwmtv7kTVDkGQGUKkp4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=d0e46c59\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/5rnw-4Fu9is</a><br />\n1989年 出道無耐 把聲好清澈響亮 好有感染力<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/9my9rDKU1wY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F9my9rDKU1wY&d=8o05Qwmtv7kTVDkGQGUKkp4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=190f0263\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/9my9rDKU1wY</a><br />\n1990年同林憶蓮合唱《還有》正到不得了 最高幾粒音真係聽出耳油<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/6L0sc3c-7mE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F6L0sc3c-7mE&d=8o05Qwmtv7kTVDkGQGUKkp4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=3ddd5775\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/6L0sc3c-7mE</a><br />\n1998年係加拿大唱《可能》把聲仲係好靚好有感染力<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/eLo1TDMKS7o\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FeLo1TDMKS7o&d=8o05Qwmtv7kTVDkGQGUKkp4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=e15613e5\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/eLo1TDMKS7o</a><br />\n1999年一返香港就聽得出有分別 把聲明顯無左以前清澈既感覺 d高音要迫出黎feel到佢有d吃力 係咪因為英皇要佢轉唱法既關係?<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/pOJArw6nrmE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FpOJArw6nrmE&d=8o05Qwmtv7kTVDkGQGUKkp4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=c281fc5a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/pOJArw6nrmE</a><br />\n2001年定02年再唱《還有》 把聲已經同之前唔同 明顯沙左好多 拆拆地<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/AY0ae2EuShk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FAY0ae2EuShk&d=8o05Qwmtv7kTVDkGQGUKkp4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=969d14c3\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/AY0ae2EuShk</a><br />\n2005年版本既《還有》把聲已經完全收皮 真係因為比人落毒?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 定係因為佢既生活習慣搞成咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d491a815b4554158c2035dca7c72f038914a07d","tid":924013,"uid":5006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T18:09:46.000Z","msg":"想聽內幕"},{"pid":"75f31fb44e15b4cf7c982fab6daed4b5e6748865","tid":924013,"uid":59961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T18:13:16.000Z","msg":"佢次次咁樣chok聲緊係啦"},{"pid":"74425ea888c7dc456bfe85df98193f8e5b14e916","tid":924013,"uid":70335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6d491a815b4554158c2035dca7c72f038914a07d","tid":924013,"uid":5006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T18:09:46.000Z","msg":"想聽內幕"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T18:43:06.000Z","msg":"我都想"},{"pid":"2640eacd24e52f546eed115099047813966f352a","tid":924013,"uid":70335,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"75f31fb44e15b4cf7c982fab6daed4b5e6748865","tid":924013,"uid":59961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T18:13:16.000Z","msg":"佢次次咁樣chok聲緊係啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T18:45:16.000Z","msg":"d人話eason把聲愈黎愈爛 但個分別點都無王傑變得咁犀利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4918880129fb0a3df106922ad002f4b8056efa2d","tid":924013,"uid":70335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T20:04:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a21e23715d1828696176f38d0311059e816a6a34","tid":924013,"uid":105838,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T20:52:45.000Z","msg":"好似比人毒過"},{"pid":"0e7fb79b3a2f4ec7d23737340656e167c48bd9da","tid":924013,"uid":31841,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T20:55:59.000Z","msg":"落咩毒呀,年紀大左唔練聲上唔到個pitch好正常<br />\n你估個